ZH: 黎明时分，太阳刚刚升起来。
EN: At dawn, the sun has just risen.

ZH: 每天黎明前，我都会喝一杯咖啡来清醒思绪。
EN: Every day before dawn, I drink a cup of coffee to clear my mind.

ZH: 黎明时，空气清新，湖面澄澈。
EN: At dawn, the air is fresh and the lake is clear.

ZH: 我非常喜欢早起看黎明的美景。
EN: I really enjoy getting up early and watching the beauty of dawn.

ZH: 黎明的微光透过窗帘洒进房间。
EN: The faint light of dawn streamed into the room through the curtains.

ZH: 黎明时刻，城市开始苏醒。
EN: At the break of dawn, the city begins to awaken.

ZH: 这是我第一次亲眼目睹那样美丽的黎明。
EN: This is the first time I have witnessed such a beautiful dawn.

ZH: 黎明的到来预示着新的一天的开始。
EN: The arrival of dawn heralds the start of a new day.

ZH: 渔民们在黎明前出海捕鱼。
EN: Fishermen set out to sea before dawn to catch fish.

ZH: 黎明的清凉空气使我感到精神焕发。
EN: The crisp morning air at dawn invigorates me.

ZH: 黎明时分的鸟鸣，是我最喜欢的声音之一。
EN: The chirping of birds at dawn is one of my favorite sounds.

ZH: 黎明的微风轻拂过脸颊，带给我宁静和平和。
EN: The gentle breeze at dawn brushes against my cheeks, bringing me tranquility and peace.

ZH: 黎明时我经常骑自行车去小山上欣赏美丽的风景。
EN: I often ride my bike to the hilltop at dawn to admire the beautiful scenery.

ZH: 黎明时分，花儿刚刚苏醒，洒上了露珠。
EN: At dawn, when the flowers are just waking up, they are covered in dewdrops.

ZH: 黎明的清凉温柔地笼罩着整个大自然。
EN: The cool and gentle dawn envelops the whole nature.

ZH: 黎明的蓝色天空让我感到无尽的希望和喜悦。
EN: The blue sky at dawn fills me with boundless hope and joy.

ZH: 黎明的阳光柔和而温暖，给予我一天的勇气和动力。
EN: The soft and warm sunlight at dawn gives me the courage and motivation for the day.

ZH: 黎明时刻，我喜欢在海滩上散步，感受清新的海风。
EN: At the break of dawn, I enjoy taking a walk on the beach, feeling the fresh sea breeze.

ZH: 黎明的美景令人心旷神怡，犹如一幅无与伦比的画作。
EN: The beauty of dawn is refreshing, like an unparalleled painting.

ZH: 黎明的第一缕阳光透过云层，照亮了大地。
EN: The first ray of sunlight at dawn breaks through the clouds and illuminates the earth.
